\id 3JN
\h 3 YONI
\toc1 YONI yana leta anaveto
\toc2 3 YONI
\mt1 YONI yana leta anaveto
\ip Hida leta againe meda Yoni ana egana keke gidayakahini tu tauna givewagana toꞋekelesiya adi Tonagona. ToꞋekelesiya saꞋeyana ana egana Gaiyasi againe giꞋetoladina. Bana tolaumamala nunuwaliliugidiyao givelugadi faꞋina gihawaveyamumuyena, tu toꞋekelesiya saꞋeyana ana egana Daiyotelefo yana dibutoyoga yana nuwalaka faꞋina gidakeyena. Leta dobona hidede amine.
\io1 Lusiule. 1:1-4
\io1 Gaiyasi ana hawaveyamumu. 1:5-8
\io1 Daiyotelefo ana dakeya. 1:9-10
\io1 Demitiliyo ana hawaveyamumu. 1:11-12
\io1 Lukafoi. 1:13-15
\c 1
\s1 ToꞋetoladi yana lusiule.
\p 
\v 1 Yo siule tobohiyaꞋaseꞋaseku Gaiyasi. Iya toꞋekelesiya adi Tonagona ya leta gaꞋetoladina be unaꞋitana.
\p 
\v 2 Ho tobohiyaku, o faꞋiniya gaveꞋoꞋola be unamiyami yamumuna, kadu aulolo keke ginavaini. AluꞋaluwa yana miyami yamumuna Yaubada matane ma a gahalamanena.
\v 3 Tobohiyadeyao tufoidi hidedei hilakayemu be valeya hilukahihiyena faꞋina nuwaku giyamumu lakahina. O faꞋiniya higahe higayo, “Nuwanuwa velemoꞋena ana muliya againe bana kaliva dibudibumuhigina. E, kadu nuwanuwa velemoꞋena againe tova moyaꞋaina gimimiyami.”
\v 4 KaꞋi natukweyao nuwanuwa velemoꞋena againe himimiyami-ma valeyadi hidede amine gananogalina, au nuwaku ginayamumu lakahina. E, hidedema againe yaku vemwamwala gitubuga-moꞋa. \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Af 19:29 \xt 1Ko 4:14-15\x*
\s1 ToꞋetoladi Gaiyasi gihawaveyamumuyena.
\p 
\v 5 TobohiyaꞋaseꞋaseku, tova moyaꞋaina tobohiyadeyao Keliso yana yoꞋo adi veluga againe o kaliva dibudibumuhigi. Kadu hiꞋelayauyoga nonogana uveluvelugadi.
\v 6 Ada badi kalivai-dina toꞋekelesiya ama yoꞋo agaimeya ya nuwanuwa hawahawahegana. Au badi Yaubada yana faisewa hiꞋabiꞋabina faꞋina, giluboda be yadina faꞋina gavadi gavadi nuwanuwadi amine, unaveledi.
\v 7 Au Keliso faꞋine tolaumamalai-dina yadi melala hihegena ada kaliva Yesu Keliso keke hidavetumaganeni-ma agaidiya keke tamo gavadi adi veluga faꞋina hidavivaini.
\v 8 Au ide tovetumagana gilubodada be hida kalivai-dina kadavelugadi be nuwanuwa velemoꞋena ana veꞋaliyahega againe ide badi buye moyaꞋaida kanakilakahina. \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Lo 12:13 \xt Af 15:3 \xt Af 20:33-35 \xt Hi 13:2\x*
\s1 ToꞋetoladi Daiyotelefo gihawavekoyoyena tu
\s1 Demitiliyo gihawaveyamumuyena.
\p 
\v 9 Tu toꞋekelesiya ana yoꞋo ya melala againe yami leta boi gaꞋetoladina, tu bana Daiyotelefo nuwanuwana lakahina ginanagoyemi-ma keke gidabonaꞋabiyeku.
\v 10 Au aimo ganaꞋela ana toveya, yana dewa omi matamiya ganayakahina, higa giveyaveyaineku tu mema gigahegahe-kawowo. Ada yana koyona giveꞋatutamoꞋaina, faꞋina tobohiyadeyao tolaumamalai-dina hilakayemu againe keke gidavetobohiyanedi, kadu badi nuwanuwadi hinavetobohiyanedi-ma gihawatadi, ada adi egana giyawelina be keke manuwa-tafalolo againe hinaluku.
\p 
\v 11 Tu tobohiyaꞋaseꞋaseku, keke huluva koyona unaveꞋuꞋuleni, au huluva yamumuna unaveꞋuꞋulena. Hai kaliva gihuluhuluva yamumuna, medema Yaubada yana kaliva. Kadu hai kaliva gihuluhuluva koyona, medema keke Yaubada gidaꞋitahalamaneni.
\p 
\v 12 Tu bana Demitiliyo ma moyaꞋaidi hihawaveyamumuyena, ada yana huluva tunutunugina faꞋina, kaliva yadi gahe bana faꞋine au velemoꞋena ma kahalamanena. Kadu ime yana huluva tunutunugina faꞋina aꞋawatalatalaina, ada ime agahe velemoꞋena ma uhalamanena. \x - \xo 1:12 \xt 1Yo 3:9-10 \xt 1Ti 3:7\x*
\s1 Leta ana lauyabu.
\p 
\v 13 Au nuwanuwaku gaitoma moyaꞋaina o againiya ganalukahihiyena tu keke nuwanuwaku feni againe ganalukahihi.
\v 14 Au ganuwaveꞋavina be tova kabiꞋona kanaveꞋamagigiꞋitaꞋita ada kanavebonanoganogala.
\v 15 Yaubada aseniwalova ginavele. Tobohiyamomo yadi nuwakabubu againiya, kadu tobohiyameyao ya melala againe yama nuwakabubu agaidiya unagaheyena.
\qr (Iya toꞋekelesiya adi Tonagona bonaku.) 
